    "Data-to-Text Assessment: For data-to-text generation, the context is highly abstract and is a list of triples in the form of (object, relation, subject).",
    "This makes assessing the semantics challenging, as the LLM needs to parse and understand semantic triples.",
    "Table 4 shows that understanding triples is an emergent ability of LLMs, where for grammar and fluency the correlations are quite similar between the 3B and 11B/13B systems, however for semantic understanding, the 10B+ systems highly outcompete the 3B+ systems.",
    "Note that when evaluating UniEval, we used the closest attribute that they designed for, which was naturalness for both.",
    "We investigate whether the comparative prompts have any implicit positional bias, and whether systems prefer the first/second position."
